altername_name: ヴァリアブル・ジオII 姫神舞闘譚
Variable Geo II: The Bout of Cabalistic Goddess
name: V.G. II: The Bout of Cabalistic Goddess
overview: After the six girls of the Jahana group have concluded their Variable Geo tournament, a girl named Kotoe Kashima, who happens to be the childhood rival of Reimi Jahana, has organized a new tournament, called "Bout of Cabalistic Goddess". The tournament is once again sponsored by a chain of restaurants, with famous martial artists working there as waitresses.
